<h3>No Parties Allowed</h3>
  <p>Parties of any kind are prohibited. Please do not disturb neighbors during quiet hours from 12:00 PM until 8:00 AM every day.</p>

  <h3>Waste Management</h3>
  <p>Please take the trash down to avoid accumulation and odors. Additional trash bags are available.</p>

  <h3>Use of Towels and Cases</h3>
  <p>Please use makeup remover pads to remove makeup; do not use the towels to clean dirt or the pillowcases to wipe off makeup.</p>

  <h3>Cleaning Kitchen Utensils</h3>
  <p>Please wash the dishes and kitchen utensils you use. A dishwasher and instructions are available in the section My accommodation -> How does it work…?</p>

  <h3>Use of Waste Bins</h3>
  <p>Please do not make more mess than normal; use the waste bins in the kitchen and bathrooms.</p>

  <h3>Pets on Furniture</h3>
  <p>Animals are strictly prohibited from climbing onto beds, sofas, and chairs. A pet bed and feeder are provided for this purpose.</p>

  <h3>Pets and Hair Cleaning</h3>
  <p>If your pet sheds a lot of hair, please use the lint roller (usually under the sink) and clean where the pet has been. We allow pets for free, but it is not right to abuse our kindness.</p>

  <h3>Do Not Take Items</h3>
  <p>It is forbidden to take things from the apartment: towels, kitchen utensils, and other belongings.</p>